        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/ee7513/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-06T14:18:16.700Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Considering such scenario in mind Signal un-linked device should show two options - Relink or Link as New. ‚ÄúRelinking will retain previous data‚Äù while ‚ÄúLinking as new‚Äù should just erase all data and start as newly linked.</p>\n<p>In any case when un-linked Signal shouldn‚Äôt show previous chats below ‚ÄòUNLINKED‚Äô as show in the SS</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/6/26059724b4ca02163b1bfc0d220bb8536468a06c.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/26059724b4ca02163b1bfc0d220bb8536468a06c\" title=\"ULINKED Screenshot from 2026-01-06 19-38-48\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/6/26059724b4ca02163b1bfc0d220bb8536468a06c_2_690x371.jpeg\" alt=\"ULINKED Screenshot from 2026-01-06 19-38-48\" data-base62-sha1=\"5qm7w88TFLnbDUoEcyXrIaV7OoY\" width=\"690\" height=\"371\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/6/26059724b4ca02163b1bfc0d220bb8536468a06c_2_690x371.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/2/6/26059724b4ca02163b1bfc0d220bb8536468a06c_2_1035x556.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/2/6/26059724b4ca02163b1bfc0d220bb8536468a06c.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"252521\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">ULINKED Screenshot from 2026-01-06 19-38-48</span><span class=\"informations\">1366√ó736 69.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>When unlinked it directly should show - Relink or Link as New (Only after Re-Linking it should show all the the previous convos) or else it just lack of privacy &amp; control. (OPSECS are OPSECS but‚Ä¶) Currently even after unlinking it just shows all the previous convos, makes no sense.</p>",
